<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Certainly you are not a God who approves of evil;</para>

<para style="q1">evil people will not be your guests.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />The arrogant will not stand in your presence;</para>

<para style="q1">you hate all who behave wickedly.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />You will destroy liars;</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh despises violent and deceitful men.</para>
